#' @param sub.d2 vectors of data in column 2
#' @param sub.d3 vectors of data in column 3
#' @param sub.d4 vectors of data in column 4
#' @param sub.d5 vectors of data in column 5
#' @param weights.1 vectors of weights of data column 1
